<head>ROAR</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">吼</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SHOUT so as to PRODUCE an INTENSELY LOUD ANIMAL NOISE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>咆哮 is the general word for the roar of an animal.</p>
<p>怒吼 focusses on the roar as a sign of anger.</p>
<p>吼</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
